configures an [emit][MutableSharedFlow.emit] action on buffer overflow. Optional, defaults to [suspending][BufferOverflow.SUSPEND] attempts to emit a value. Values other than [BufferOverflow.SUSPEND] are supported only when `replay > 0` or `extraBufferCapacity > 0`. In the absence of subscribers only the most recent [replay] values are stored and the buffer overflow behavior is never triggered and has no effect.
